sub offer first desktop:
In addition to cloud storage, increased Force Build save slots, and the ability to access your saved forces across multiple devices, with a subscription to the Warmachine app you will receive exclusive content delivered weekly to your app library.

Explore the Forces of Warmachine and the rich lore of the Iron Kingdoms, unlock new ways to play the game through the ongoing campaign and all new scenarios, and immerse yourself in the epic fiction that brings the pantheon of Warmachine characters to life.

Subscriptions are available on iOs and Google Play devices.  Once you have made a Warmachine App account and subscribed, your upgraded account will be available on all platforms you use your Warmachine App account on.
